#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Validates a dependency import status variable. A valid dependency import
# status variable must:
#   - Be defined
#   - Not be empty
#   - Be a boolean with value of '1' (found) or '0' (not found)
#
# Signature:
#   validate_dep_import_status(<output-result-var>
#                              <out-err-msg-var>
#                              <error-on-fail>
#                              <input-value>)
#
# Parameters:
